  <section id="ircmeetingtime">
    <title>IRC Meeting Time</title>

    <para>This project&#39;s developers meet regularly to discuss issues such
    as design. At the time of writing, developers meet weekly at
    <emphasis>19:30 Monday UTC</emphasis>. Check <ulink
    url="http://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/">http://www.timeanddate.com/worldclock/</ulink>
    to find what this time translates to in your part of the world.</para>

    <para>Members of the Project Management Committee (PMC) who are regular
    IRC participants should let others know if they are not coming so that the
    meeting is not delayed on their behalf.</para>
  </section>
